OL,3,CMan accused of Natalie McNally's
OL,4,Cmurder will not take the stand
OL,6,FThe man accused of murdering his
OL,7,Fpregnant girlfriend Natalie McNally in
OL,8,FDecember 2022 will not take the stand.
OL,10,FThe defence told the Judge they would
OL,11,Fnot be calling any evidence on behalf
OL,12,Fof Stephen McCullagh.
OL,14,FThe 36-year-old of Woodland Gardens in
OL,15,FLisburn, is on trial at Belfast Crown
OL,16,FCourt accused of murder.
OL,18,FHe has denied the charge.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/6
