OL,3,CMan accused of Natalie McNally's
OL,4,Cmurder will not take the stand
OL,6,FOn Monday, the who lead the murder
OL,7,Finvestigation was also questioned
OL,8,Fabout messages sent between the pair.
OL,10,FThe Court heard that he was surprised
OL,11,Fat the lack of affection in the texts,
OL,12,Fsomething the defence disputed.
OL,14,FDuring cross examination, the defence
OL,15,Fskimmed through 500 pages of WhatsApp
OL,16,Fmessages between the defendant and Ms
OL,17,FMcNally over 133 days between August
OL,18,Fand December 2022.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
