OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773778273
OL,3,CMan accused of Natalie McNally's
OL,4,Cmurder will not take the stand
OL,6,FStephen McCullagh told Natalie she was
OL,7,Fthe "loveliest, sweetest person he had
OL,8,Fever met".
OL,10,FFollowing their first pregnancy scan
OL,11,Fin November 2022, he texted her, "I
OL,12,Flove you and the squish and I don't
OL,13,Fwant anything to happen to either of
OL,14,Fyou".
OL,16,FNatalie was found dead on 19 December,
OL,17,Fit is believed she suffered a
OL,18,Fprolonged assault.
OL,20,FThe Jury heard there were no injuries
OL,21,Fon the defendant's hands.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
